## GAP 3: Heartbeat Handler Logging on First Receive

The Go code logs at INFO level when a first heartbeat is received. The Rust code does not.

### Go Code (`/tmp/tork-go/internal/coordinator/handlers/heartbeat.go` lines 24-30):
```go
func (h *heartbeatHandler) handle(ctx context.Context, n *tork.Node) error {
    _, err := h.ds.GetNodeByID(ctx, n.ID)
    if err == datastore.ErrNodeNotFound {
        log.Info().
            Str("node-id", n.ID).
            Str("hostname", n.Hostname).
            Msg("received first heartbeat")
        return h.ds.CreateNode(ctx, n)
    }
